Package: CloudFlux
Title: Point Cloud Change Detection and Mapping
Version: 0.1.0.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("Christopher", "Scarpone", , "chris.scarpone@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Lidar Tool that is designed to help foresters, scientists, citizen scientists, and anyone who is curious enough to explore. The tool combines most pre-processing, processing, and post-processing procedures for any point cloud, raster, and shapefile data in the click of a few buttons.
